Adam Fleming is a Scottish news reporter , best known for his work on CBBC 's news programme , Newsround . He also reports for Sportsround , and as a reporter for BBC News 24 . As a teenager Adam had the opportunity to direct some productions for the Scottish Youth Theatre . He has done journalism work for The Herald newspaper in Glasgow , The Daily Record and Scottish Television . He went to Hertford College , Oxford where he studied Geography and was able to edit The Oxford Student newspaper . He graduated from Oxford University in 2001 , with a first class degree . He was sponsored by BBC News on a postgraduate Diploma in Broadcast Journalism at City University , London . This BBC - related article is a stub . 